1 Summary: before & after

Exluding criteria:

  • chr == 2 & pos_start < 6e6 (beginning of chr)
  • chr == 6 & pos_start > 29e6 & pos_start < 34e6 (MHC)
  • chr == 11 & pos_start < 2e6 (beginning of chr)
